lem\u00f3w z wy\u015bwietlaniem zdj\u0119\u0107 na Amazonie.<\/li>\n<li><b>Optymalizuj zdj\u0119cia.<\/b> Upewnij si\u0119, \u017ce Twoje zdj\u0119cia s\u0105 odpowiednio zoptymalizowane pod k\u0105tem jako\u015bci i rozmiaru. Dobre zdj\u0119cia mog\u0105 przyci\u0105gn\u0105\u0107 wi\u0119cej klient\u00f3w i zwi\u0119kszy\u0107 Twoje szanse na sprzeda\u017c.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Podsumowuj\u0105c, hostowanie zdj\u0119\u0107 w Amazonie nie musi by\u0107 skomplikowane. Wybieraj\u0105c odpowiedni\u0105 platform\u0119 i przestrzegaj\u0105c prostych krok\u00f3w, mo\u017cesz poprawi\u0107 jako\u015b\u0107 prezentacji swoich produkt\u00f3w.<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h2>Jak efektywnie hostowa\u0107 linki do zdj\u0119\u0107 w Amazonie?<\/h2>\n<p>Czy zastanawia\u0142e\u015b si\u0119, jak najlepiej za<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":5666,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[2],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-5665","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-kontent"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5665"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=5665"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5665\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/5666"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=5665"}],"wp:term":[{"taxono